&lt;p&gt;Andreas, do you plan to backport fix into 2.15 line?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve cherry-picked it as patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/54671&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/54671&lt;/a&gt; but I can&apos;t say when it will land.  The patch applied cleanly without any manual intervention, so you could apply it to your own code as needed with little effort.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
